       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI68700.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI68700.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Lista Despesas Respons嫛el - Detalhe                       *
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI68700         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD4804 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5303 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV6870.
       COPY COCV6871.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.
       COPY AQCW0005.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            SWITCH
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  SW-SWITCH.
           05 SW-CURSOR                  PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.
              88 SW-CURSOR-NONE                    VALUE '0'.
              88 SW-CURSOR-1                       VALUE '1'.
              88 SW-CURSOR-2                       VALUE '2'.
              88 SW-CURSOR-3                       VALUE '3'.
              88 SW-CURSOR-4                       VALUE '3'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COVT4804 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT4804'.
           05 CON-COVT5303 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT5303'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-IND                    PIC  9(10).

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME     PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI68700'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *              DECLARACOES DE CURSORES DB2                     *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CURSOR-VARS.
           05 WS-DTMESANO-MIN           PIC  X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DTMESANO-MIN.
              10 WS-ANO-MIN             PIC  X(04)  VALUE SPACES.
              10 WS-T1-MIN              PIC  X(01)  VALUE '-'.
              10 WS-MES-MIN             PIC  X(02)  VALUE SPACES.
              10 WS-T2-MIN              PIC  X(01)  VALUE '-'.
              10 WS-DIA-MIN             PIC  X(02)  VALUE '01'.

           05 WS-DTMESANO-MAX           PIC  X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DTMESANO-MAX.
              10 WS-ANO-MAX             PIC  X(04)  VALUE SPACES.
              10 WS-T1-MAX              PIC  X(01)  VALUE '-'.
              10 WS-MES-MAX             PIC  X(02)  VALUE SPACES.
              10 WS-T2-MAX              PIC  X(01)  VALUE '-'.
              10 WS-DIA-MAX             PIC  X(02)  VALUE '01'.

           05 FILLER                    PIC  X(01) VALUE SPACES.

           EXEC SQL
                DECLARE CURCOT01 CURSOR FOR
                 SELECT
                        CIDEMP
                      , DTMESANO
                      , CIDDESP
                      , TIPODESPESA
                      , MVLR
                      , DTREG
                      , CMOED
                      , MCAMBDIA
                      , MCONTRVLR
                      , CIDCLIENTE
                      , GCLIENTE
                      , CIDPROJ
                      , GPROJ
                      , NSEQ
                      , GOBSERV
                      , CUSERAPR
                      , DDTAPR
                      , CSITU
                      , CEMPRESA
                   FROM COVT4804_EXPENSE
                  WHERE ( NSEQ     >= :COCD4804-NSEQ )
                    AND   CEMPRESA  = :COCD4804-CEMPRESA
                    AND   CIDEMP    = :COCD4804-CIDEMP
                    AND   DTMESANO  = :COCD4804-DTMESANO
                    AND   CIDPROJ   = :COCD4804-CIDPROJ
                    AND   CMOED     = :COCD4804-CMOED
               ORDER BY CEMPRESA
                      , CIDEMP
                      , DTMESANO
                      , CIDPROJ
                      , CMOED
                      , NSEQ
           END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI68700         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------

       COPY VIAL0004.

            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.

           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV6870-MSG.
           MOVE COCV6870-ASE               TO COCV6871-ASE.

           INITIALIZE WS-VARIAVEIS
                      COCV6871-ADE          REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                                 ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.

       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV6870-ADE                TO COCV6871-ADE.

           PERFORM 2010-VALIDACOES
              THRU 2019-VALIDACOES-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2020-OPEN
                 THRU 2029-OPEN-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2030-FETCH
                 THRU 2039-FETCH-EXIT

              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 IF DB2-OK
                    PERFORM 2040-CONTINUA
                       THRU 2049-CONTINUA-EXIT
                 ELSE
                    COMPUTE COCV6871-DIMINUI-LENGTH =
                            COCV6871-INDICE-INVERSO *
                            COCV6871-LENGTH-OCCUR
                    COMPUTE COCV6871-LENGTH =
                            COCV6871-LENGTH -
                            COCV6871-DIMINUI-LENGTH

                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO COCV6871-CFUNCIONARIO-S
                    MOVE COCK0001-EXPENSE-N-EXISTS
                      TO COCV6871-CFUNCIONARIO-MSG
                    MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                      TO COCV6871-CFUNCIONARIO-CAPLIC
                 END-IF
              END-IF

              PERFORM 2070-CLOSE
                 THRU 2079-CLOSE-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2010-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2010-VALIDACOES.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2010-VALIDACOES' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV6870-CEMPRESA       TO COCD4804-CEMPRESA.
           MOVE COCV6870-CFUNCIONARIO   TO COCD4804-CIDEMP.
           MOVE COCV6870-DTMESANO       TO COCD4804-DTMESANO.
           MOVE COCV6870-CIDPROJ        TO COCD4804-CIDPROJ.
           MOVE COCV6870-CMOED          TO COCD4804-CMOED.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2010-VALIDACOES-EXIT'      TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV6870-NSEQ-PAG          TO COCD4804-NSEQ.

       2019-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2020-OPEN
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2020-OPEN.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2020-OPEN' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
               OPEN CURCOT01
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT4804               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

       2029-OPEN-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2030-FETCH
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2030-FETCH.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2030-FETCH' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
              FETCH CURCOT01
              INTO
                  :COCD4804-CIDEMP
                , :COCD4804-DTMESANO
                , :COCD4804-CIDDESP
                , :COCD4804-TIPODESPESA
                , :COCD4804-MVLR
                , :COCD4804-DTREG
                , :COCD4804-CMOED
                , :COCD4804-MCAMBDIA
                , :COCD4804-MCONTRVLR
                , :COCD4804-CIDCLIENTE
                , :COCD4804-GCLIENTE
                , :COCD4804-CIDPROJ
                , :COCD4804-GPROJ
                , :COCD4804-NSEQ
                , :COCD4804-GOBSERV
                , :COCD4804-CUSERAPR
                , :COCD4804-DDTAPR
                , :COCD4804-CSITU
                , :COCD4804-CEMPRESA
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-COVT4804               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

       2039-FETCH-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                       2040-CONTINUA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2040-CONTINUA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2040-CONTINUA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ZEROES                     TO COCV6871-INDICE.
           PERFORM 2050-TRATA-OCCURS
              THRU 2059-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT
             UNTIL DB2-NOTFND
                OR COCV6871-PAGINA-CHEIA
                OR NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF NOT COCV6871-PAGINA-CHEIA
                    COMPUTE COCV6871-INDICE-INVERSO EQUAL
                         COCV6871-INDICE-INVERSO - COCV6871-INDICE
                    COMPUTE COCV6871-DIMINUI-LENGTH EQUAL
                         COCV6871-INDICE-INVERSO * COCV6871-LENGTH-OCCUR
                    COMPUTE COCV6871-LENGTH EQUAL COCV6871-LENGTH -
                         COCV6871-DIMINUI-LENGTH
                    SET  VIAL0002-FIM-CONSULTA TO TRUE
              END-IF
              IF DB2-NOTFND
                    SET  VIAL0002-FIM-CONSULTA TO TRUE
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2049-CONTINUA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2050-TRATA-OCCURS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2050-TRATA-OCCURS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2050-TRATA-OCCURS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           ADD 1 TO COCV6871-INDICE.

           MOVE COCD4804-NSEQ         TO COCV6871-D-NSEQ
                                         (COCV6871-INDICE).
           MOVE COCD4804-CIDDESP      TO COCV6871-D-TIPODESPESA
                                         (COCV6871-INDICE).
           MOVE COCD4804-MVLR         TO COCV6871-D-MVLR
                                         (COCV6871-INDICE).
           MOVE COCD4804-DTREG        TO COCV6871-D-DTREG
                                         (COCV6871-INDICE).
           MOVE COCD4804-MCAMBDIA     TO COCV6871-D-CAMBIO
                                         (COCV6871-INDICE).
           MOVE COCD4804-GOBSERV      TO COCV6871-D-GOBSERV
                                         (COCV6871-INDICE).
           MOVE COCD4804-CUSERAPR     TO COCV6871-D-CAPROVADO
                                         (COCV6871-INDICE).
           MOVE COCD4804-DDTAPR       TO COCV6871-D-DTAPROV
                                         (COCV6871-INDICE).
           MOVE COCD4804-CSITU        TO COCV6871-D-CSITDSP
                                         (COCV6871-INDICE).
           MOVE COCD4804-MCONTRVLR    TO COCV6871-D-CTRVLR
                                         (COCV6871-INDICE).

           PERFORM 2030-FETCH
              THRU 2039-FETCH-EXIT.

       2059-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2070-CLOSE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2070-CLOSE.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2070-CLOSE' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
               CLOSE CURCOT01
           END-EXEC.

       2079-CLOSE-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV6871-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV6871-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV6871-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE COCV6871-INDICE            TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0016.
